    * _I_n_s_t_i_t_u_t_e_ _f_o_r_ _O_p_e_r_a_t_i_o_n_s_ _R_e_s_e_a_r_c_h_ _a_n_d_ _t_h_e_ _M_a_n_a_g_e_m_e_n_t_ _S_c_i_e_n_c_e_s (INFORMS)
